  # Ecommerce Backend API Collection
  
  This Bruno collection contains comprehensive API tests for the ecommerce backend system.
  
  ## Available Endpoints:
  
  ### üè• Health Check
  - GET /api/healthz - System health check
  
  ### üë• Users (6 endpoints)
  - POST /api/users - Create user
  - GET /api/users - Get all users (paginated)
  - GET /api/users/{id} - Get user by ID
  - PUT /api/users/{id} - Update user
  - DELETE /api/users/{id} - Delete user
  
  ### üìÇ Categories (6 endpoints)
  - POST /api/categories - Create category
  - GET /api/categories - Get all categories
  - GET /api/categories/tree - Get category tree
  - GET /api/categories/{id} - Get category by ID
  - PUT /api/categories/{id} - Update category
  - DELETE /api/categories/{id} - Delete category
  
  ### üì¶ Products (6 endpoints)
  - POST /api/products - Create product
  - GET /api/products - Get all products (with filters)
  - GET /api/products/{id} - Get product by ID
  - GET /api/products/slug/{slug} - Get product by slug
  - PUT /api/products/{id} - Update product
  - DELETE /api/products/{id} - Delete product
  
  ### üìç Addresses (5 endpoints)
  - POST /api/addresses - Create address
  - GET /api/addresses/user/{userId} - Get user addresses
  - GET /api/addresses/{id} - Get address by ID
  - PUT /api/addresses/{id} - Update address
  - DELETE /api/addresses/{id} - Delete address
  
  ### üìã Orders (6 endpoints)
  - POST /api/orders - Create order
  - GET /api/orders - Get all orders (with filters)
  - GET /api/orders/{id} - Get order by ID
  - GET /api/orders/number/{orderNumber} - Get order by number
  - PUT /api/orders/{id}/status - Update order status
  - PUT /api/orders/{id}/cancel - Cancel order
  
  ### üõí Carts (15 endpoints)
  - POST /api/carts - Create cart
  - GET /api/carts/{id} - Get cart by ID
  - GET /api/carts/user/{userId} - Get/create user cart
  - GET /api/carts/guest/{sessionId} - Get/create guest cart
  - POST /api/carts/{id}/add - Add item to cart
  - PUT /api/carts/items/{itemId} - Update cart item
  - DELETE /api/carts/items/{itemId} - Remove cart item
  - DELETE /api/carts/{id}/clear - Clear cart
  - POST /api/carts/merge - Merge carts
  - GET /api/carts/{id}/stats - Get cart statistics
  - GET /api/carts/{id}/count - Get cart count
  - GET /api/carts/{id}/validate - Validate cart
  - GET /api/carts/{id}/checkout-summary - Get checkout summary
  - GET /api/carts/{id}/prepare-order - Prepare for order
  - POST /api/carts/cleanup - Cleanup expired carts
  
  ### üîç Search (7 endpoints)
  - GET /api/search/products - Advanced product search with filters
  - GET /api/search/suggestions - Search autocomplete suggestions
  - GET /api/search/filters - Available search filters
  - GET /api/search/popular-terms - Popular search terms
  - GET /api/search/trending - Trending products
  - GET /api/search/related/{productId} - Related products
  - GET /api/search/recently-viewed - Recently viewed products
  
  ### ‚≠ê Reviews & Ratings (10 endpoints)
  - POST /api/reviews - Create product review
  - GET /api/reviews/products/{productId} - Get product reviews
  - GET /api/reviews/{reviewId} - Get review by ID
  - POST /api/reviews/{reviewId}/helpful - Mark review helpful/not helpful
  - GET /api/reviews/products/{productId}/summary - Get rating summary
  - POST /api/reviews/questions - Create product question
  - GET /api/reviews/products/{productId}/questions - Get product questions
  - POST /api/reviews/questions/{questionId}/answers - Create answer
  - GET /api/reviews/questions/{questionId}/answers - Get question answers
  - GET /api/reviews/statistics - Review statistics (admin)
  
  ### üé´ Coupons & Discounts (12 endpoints)
  - POST /api/coupons - Create coupon (admin)
  - GET /api/coupons - Get coupons with filters (admin)
  - GET /api/coupons/public - Get public coupons for display
  - GET /api/coupons/my-coupons - Get user's available coupons
  - POST /api/coupons/validate - Validate coupon for cart
  - POST /api/coupons/apply - Apply coupon to cart
  - POST /api/coupons/remove - Remove coupon from cart
  - GET /api/coupons/{couponId} - Get coupon by ID (admin)
  - PUT /api/coupons/{couponId} - Update coupon (admin)
  - DELETE /api/coupons/{couponId} - Delete coupon (admin)
  - POST /api/coupons/assign - Assign coupon to users (admin)
  - GET /api/coupons/statistics - Coupon statistics (admin)
  
  ### üîß Admin Panel (19 endpoints)
  - GET /api/admin/dashboard - Dashboard analytics
  - GET /api/admin/analytics/{type} - Detailed analytics
  - GET /api/admin/orders - Admin order management
  - GET /api/admin/products - Admin product management
  - GET /api/admin/customers - Admin customer management
  - PUT /api/admin/products/bulk - Bulk product operations
  - PUT /api/admin/inventory/bulk - Bulk inventory updates
  - PUT /api/admin/orders/bulk - Bulk order updates
  - GET /api/admin/stats/orders - Order statistics
  - GET /api/admin/stats/system - System statistics
  - GET /api/admin/inventory/low-stock - Low stock products
  - GET /api/admin/activity/recent - Recent activity
  - GET /api/admin/notifications - Admin notifications
  - GET /api/admin/reports - Generate reports (JSON/CSV)
  - POST /api/admin/maintenance/cleanup-carts - Cleanup carts
  
  ## Environment Variables:
  - baseURL: http://localhost:4000 (configured in local.bru)
  
  ## Usage:
  1. Start the server: npm run dev
  2. Select 'local' environment in Bruno
  3. Run individual requests or entire folders
  4. Check response data and status codes
  
  ## Authentication:
  Currently all endpoints are set to 'auth: none' for testing.
  Update individual requests to add authentication when implemented.
